# Project Overview: Telecine Video Processing System

## Tier 1: High-Level Architecture

Telecine is a sophisticated video processing and playback system built as a SaaS platform. The system supports real-time playback of arbitrary video URLs with just-in-time transcoding capabilities.

### Core Capabilities
- **Video Playback**: Real-time playback component for web applications
- **Video Processing**: FFmpeg-based transcoding with seekable format support
- **File Management**: Upload, processing, and storage of video/audio/image files
- **Rendering Pipeline**: HTML-to-video rendering with distributed worker architecture
- **Transcription**: Audio transcription with fragment-based processing
- **API-First**: RESTful APIs with GraphQL integration via Hasura

### Technology Stack
- **Frontend**: React 18 + Remix (React Router v7) + TypeScript
- **Backend**: Node.js + Express + PostgreSQL + Hasura GraphQL
- **Video Processing**: FFmpeg 6.1 + Custom C++ Node.js addon
- **Infrastructure**: Docker + Microservices architecture
- **Real-time**: WebSockets + Server-Sent Events
- **Storage**: Google Cloud Storage integration
- **Queue System**: Redis/Valkey-based job prcessing

## Tier 2: Directory Structure

### `/lib/` - Shared Libraries
Core business logic and utilities shared across services:
- `packages/` - **Separate symlinked repository** for browser-side video processing components (distributed independently on npm)
- `transcode/` - C++ FFmpeg integration for video processing
- `render/` - Video rendering engines and encoding controllers
- `sql-client.server/` - Database client and migrations
- `graphql/` & `graphql.server/` & `graphql.client/` - GraphQL integration layers
- `queues/` - Job queue management
- `process-file/` - File processing utilities
- `logging/` - Centralized logging system
- `util/` - General utilities

### `/services/` - Microservices
Distributed services for different concerns:
- `web/` - Main Remix web application (frontend + backend)
- `worker-*` - Specialized worker services:
  - `worker-render-initializer/` - Render job initialization
  - `worker-render-fragment/` - Video fragment rendering
  - `worker-render-finalizer/` - Render job completion
  - `worker-process-isobmff/` - ISO Base Media File Format processing
  - `worker-process-html-*` - HTML processing pipeline
  - `worker-ingest-image/` - Image file ingestion
- `scheduler/` - Job scheduling service
- `transcribe/` & `transcribe-ctl/` - Audio transcription services
- `render/` - Core rendering service
- `dev-*` - Development environment services (postgres, valkey, etc.)
- `graphql-engine/` - Hasura GraphQL engine configuration

### `/tests/` - Testing Infrastructure
- `@editframe/api/` - API client tests
- `playwright/` - End-to-end browser tests
- `util/` - Testing utilities and helpers

